{"tid":1965460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色經濟圈］靠手足喺連登推po同fb share成功救左間綠轉黃嘅公司","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T19:26:21.000Z","uid":170426,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"065dc1f88e08679b8960d035b0f87e9eb487d16b","tid":1965460,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"繼上個po:<br />\n［黃色經濟圈］有公司由東方轉去蘋果登廣告但生意大減 希望大家支持<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1961111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1961111</a><br />\n<br />\n好多手足幫手推po俾左好多意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔少人都有提議試下AM730<br />\n估唔到真係成功左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5NukN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5NukN7.png&h=c6a0fd20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想喺度鼓勵同多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然每日都見到五毛出沒好撚煩<br />\n但呢度仍然係一個俾大家討論空間嘅好地方<br />\n而我地每一個喺度推po,留cm,share<br />\n其實都有影響<br />\n希望大家唔好放棄<br />\n你永遠唔知道今日做嘅野會帶黎乜野影響<br />\n<br />\n大家加油 連仔加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"59a44b2f5afa5a26b1dbf5ce89003b9e45a50ed4","tid":1965460,"uid":170426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"希望連登唔使淨係屌人分化撚失敗撚<br />\n大家可以正面一齊繼續抗爭"},{"pid":"3252040610fc0c95be0beaf8a90f444aeb984431","tid":1965460,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"士氣po<br />\n求推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb9c47d67f7fcef0fb0b04b1a37b6501793be29","tid":1965460,"uid":283912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"證明Be humble同唔鬥黃好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23db7b0576cba9ad1aae12af52918e08025b4